<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>218</hymn_number>
<title>THANGTHATNAK A UM HNGA MAW? CH218</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Vancung a tha a ceu khua khi ka ruat ni-hin, Ni tlak tik ka tlunnak
 ding khua khi, Khamhtu dawtnak thawngin khi ram ka phak tikah, Sunparnak
 kei ca a um hnga maw?

[C1]
   Thangthatnak kei ca a um hnga maw? Vawlei cung ka nunnak ni a liam
   tikah cun, (tikah cun) Zungzal kaa dinhnak inn tha ka phak khawh tikah,
   Thangthatnak kei ca a um hnga maw? (um hnga maw)

[V2]
 Ka tuan khawh tiang Bawipa hngatchan in ka tuan lai, Thlarau tlaitu ah
 run ka ser tuah, A-mah sunparnak hmaiah khin ka dir tikah, Thangthat kha
 kei ca a si nakhnga.

[C2]
   Thangthatnak kei ca a um hnga maw? Vawlei cung ka nunnak ni a liam
   tikah cun, (tikah cun) Zungzal kaa dinhnak inn tha ka phak khawh tikah,
   Thangthatnak kei ca a um hnga maw? (um hnga maw)

[V3]
 Bawipa ka hmuh tikah ka lunglawmhnak vialte, Zeitluk in dah ka chim
 khawh te hnga, Aa dawh le a ceu sui khua tha ka phak tikah, Thangthat le
 sunpar kei ca si cang.

[C3]
   Thangthatnak kei ca a um hnga maw? Vawlei cung ka nunnak ni a liam
   tikah cun, (tikah cun) Zungzal kaa dinhnak inn tha ka phak khawh tikah,
   Thangthatnak kei ca a um hnga maw? (um hnga maw)</lyrics>
<key>A</key>
</song>